TO compile all: make all

To compile sqlite code, use "-lsqlite3"

------------------------------
11/2/2015
How to use ssl_server?
=========================

Listening port:
***************
ssl_common.h:#define PORT "6001"

The student login records:
***************************
ssl_common.h:#define STUDENT_LOGIN_RECORD "cs535_student_login_records.txt"


The DB name is defined in:
*************************
sqlite_db.h:#define DB_NAME "CS535.db"
sqlite_db.h:#define TABLE_NAME "CS535_student_table"


The server cert and CA names are defined in:
*********************************************
ssl_server.c:#define SERVERCERT "cs535_server_cert_fall14.pem"
ssl_server.c:#define CAFILE "cs535_CA_cert_fall14.pem"


